data.description: Spacious Open Ranch with Split Bedroom Concept in Knottingham Subdivision! The Owners had Bart Denlinger Custom Build this Home Specifically for their Primitive Antiques! Inviting Covered Front Porch with Swing. Large Open Great Room with Gas Fireplace! Spacious Kitchen Dining Area! 4x8 Pantry. Range, Refrigerator and Dishwasher. Lovely 12x13 All Seasons Room. Spacious Bedroom Suite with Walk-in Closet and Tub Shower Bath on the West Side of the House. Laundry Room with a Closet and Washer and Dryer. Two Roomy Bedrooms on the Opposite Side and Center Hall Bath Between with a Large Walk-In Shower. Spacious Rear Yard with Patio and Storage Shed. Rainbird Irrigation System and Well for Watering the Lawn. Extra Wide Drive and Parking Pad Beside the House. This Home Was Wheel-Chair Accessible. Schedule Your Appointment Today Before This Great Miami East School District Home Gets Away!
